'''Teroch Squad''' (''teroch'' means ''pitiless'' in [[Mando'a/Legends|Mando'a]], language of the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorians]]) was a [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commando]] squad that fought in the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]]. The only known member was [[Fi Skirata|RC-8015]], or "Fi", who was the only survivor in Teroch Squad following that battle. He later served in [[Omega Squad]]. The squad was trained by [[Kal Skirata]].

